        <p>Aṭaiyāṟu-nāṭu ma <lb break="no" n="4"></lb>l<unclear>ai</unclear>yaṉṉār āḷa Orukil maṇaṟ <lb break="no" n="5"></lb>-c-cuṉai mēṟ paṭai vara Ūr Aḻiy<unclear>ā</unclear> <lb break="no" n="6"></lb>maiy kāttu paṭṭāṉ catti <lb n="7"></lb>ma <unclear>va</unclear>kilavaṉ v<choice>
